#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid "This information is a great help to the Debian project. It is used to determine which packages should go on the first installation disks. The installation data is also an important factor used to decide whether to remove a package with very few users from the distribution. We heartily recommend installing the <emphasis role=\"pkg\">popularity-contest</emphasis> package, and participating to the survey."
msgstr "此类信息对 Debian 项目是很有用的。将会决定哪些软件包出现在首个安装盘上。此类信息也是决定是否移除某些只有少数用户使用软件包的重要因素。我们衷心的希望安装<emphasis role=\"pkg\">popularity-contest</emphasis> 软件包，并参与调查。"

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid "The collected data are made public every day. <ulink type=\"block\" url=\"http://popcon.debian.org/\" />"
